    SELECT [s0].[Id], [s0].[Charge_Amt], [s0].[Charge_Type], [s0].[Co_Code], [s0].[CreatedDate], [s0].[CreatedUser], [s0].[CreditAcc], [s0].[CustomerId], [s0].[CustomerName], [s0].[DebitAcc], [s0].[FT_Id], [s0].[InMoneyUser], [s0].[IsActive], [s0].[MoneyAtAcc], [s0].[MoneyChangeDate], [s0].[OrgCode], [s0].[OrgName], [s0].[OrganizationId], [s0].[OutTransactionHeaderId], [s0].[PAN_NUMBER], [s0].[Payment_Detail], [s0].[Phone_Number], [s0].[RRN], [s0].[Rc_code], [s0].[Refund_Ref], [s0].[Return_Acc], [s0].[SourceType], [s0].[StatusLine], [s0].[Tien_hoan], [s0].[TotalMoneyAcc], [s0].[Total_Amt], [s0].[TraceId], [s0].[Trans_Amt], [s0].[Trans_Date], [s0].[Trans_Time], [s0].[Trans_type], [s0].[UpdatedDate], [s0].[UpdatedUser], [s0].[UserRc_code]
    FROM [SB_OutTransactionDetails] AS [s0]
    WHERE [s0].[StatusLine] = 2
) AS [t] ON [s].[Id] = [t].[OutTransactionHeaderId]
WHERE ((CONVERT(date, [s].[DateTrans]) = '2022-11-17T00:00:00.0000000') AND ([s].[Status] = N'outApprove')) AND ([s].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit))
ORDER BY [s].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[Id]"

[g0].[UpdatedUser]
FROM [GF_Booking] AS [g]
INNER JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [g].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [C_Course] AS [c] ON [g].[C_Course_Id] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [C_Org] AS [c0] ON [g].[C_Org_Id] = [c0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [GF_BookingLine] AS [g0] ON [g].[Id] = [g0].[GF_Booking_Id]

INSERT ([Charge_Amt], [Charge_Type], [Co_Code], [CreatedDate], [CreatedUser], [CreditAcc], [CustomerId], [CustomerName], [DebitAcc], [FT_Id], [InMoneyUser], [IsActive], [MoneyAtAcc], [MoneyChangeDate], [OrgCode], [OrgName], [OrganizationId], [OutTransactionHeaderId], [PAN_NUMBER], [Payment_Detail], [Phone_Number], [RRN], [Rc_code], [Refund_Ref], [Return_Acc], [SourceType], [StatusLine], [Tien_hoan], [TotalMoneyAcc], [Total_Amt], [TraceId], [Trans_Amt], [Trans_Date], [Trans_Time], [Trans_type], [UpdatedDate], [UpdatedUser], [UserRc_code])
VALUES (i.[Charge_Amt], i.[Charge_Type], i.[Co_Code], i.[CreatedDate], i.[CreatedUser], i.[CreditAcc], i.[CustomerId], i.[CustomerName], i.[DebitAcc], i.[FT_Id], i.[InMoneyUser], i.[IsActive], i.[MoneyAtAcc], i.[MoneyChangeDate], i.[OrgCode], i.[OrgName], i.[OrganizationId], i.[OutTransactionHeaderId], i.[PAN_NUMBER], i.[Payment_Detail], i.[Phone_Number], i.[RRN], i.[Rc_code], i.[Refund_Ref], i.[Return_Acc], i.[SourceType], i.[StatusLine], i.[Tien_hoan], i.[TotalMoneyAcc], i.[Total_Amt], i.[TraceId], i.[Trans_Amt], i.[Trans_Date], i.[Trans_Time], i.[Trans_type], i.[UpdatedDate], i.[UpdatedUser], i.[UserRc_code])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [t].[Id] FROM [SB_OutTransactionDetails] t
INNER JOIN @inserted0 i ON ([t].[Id] = [i].[Id])
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];"

To identify the code which triggers this warning, call 'ConfigureWarnings(w => w.Throw(RelationalEventId.SavepointsDisabledBecauseOfMARS))'.

To identify the code which triggers this warning, call 'ConfigureWarnings(w => w.Throw(RelationalEventId.SavepointsDisabledBecauseOfMARS))'.

To identify the code which triggers this warning, call 'ConfigureWarnings(w => w.Throw(RelationalEventId.SavepointsDisabledBecauseOfMARS))'.
